  "title": "Light Pungent Algerian Doraji Tagine",
  "description": "A pungent and light Algerian dish featuring bellflower root doraji, cooked in a clay pot, perfect for a low glycemic brunch, this recipe brings the unique flavors of North Africa to your table with a delicate balance of spices and ingredients.",
