  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a clay pot, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced doraji and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the ground cumin, coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Cover the clay pot and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the doraji is tender.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
